	   <tr><td colspan=2>I SEEM TO NOTICE A COMPLETE LACK OF USEFUL INFORMATION ABOUT THE UPCOMING BEASTMASTER CLASS.&nbsp;&nbsp;I (LIKE EVERY OTHER FOOL OUT THERE NO DOUBT) PLAN ON MAKING A BEASTMASTER AND HAVE ALREADY BEGUN COLLECTING GEAR FOR MY UPCOMING HERO.  FROM THE GEAR I'VE COLLECTED ALONE I CAN TELL YOU THIS MUCH, THEY WILL MOST LIKELY BE A MONK/SHAMMY CROSS (WHICH IS ABOUT THE ONLY USEFUL INFO STATED IN ANY OF THE OTHER POST THUS FAR) WEAPONS SKILLS I'VE BEEN ABLE TO CONFIRM SO FAR ARE PIERCING/1HB/2HB.  IT ALSO APPEARS THAT THEY WILL GET TO DUEL WIELD. (ONE PIERCER IS OFF HAND ONLY AND HAS BST AS USEABLE CLASS) AS THEY ARE MONK, I IMAGINE THEY WILL HAVE CONSIDERABLE HAND2HAND AS WELL.  SPELLS ARE VERY PET BASED SO FAR.  THEIR ABILITY TO HEAL APPEARS TO BE LIMITED TO THEIR PET ONLY, BUT GOOD NEWS IS THEY CAN HEAL FAR BETTER THAN A SHAMMY OR DRUID (EVEN GET COMPLETE PET HEAL AT 55) HAVE A WIDE VARIETY OF PET BUFFS, INCLUDING A LARGE LINE OF BASE STATS/LEVEL BUFF, PET HASTES STR AND SO ON.  PROBABLY THE COOLEST THING ABOUT THEIR PET BUFFS IS THAT PET PROCS A HUGE VARIETY OF DD'S DEPENDING ON BUFF GIVEN.<br>CHECK OUT THIS WEBSITE(NOTHING IS CONCRETE TILL EXPANSION COMES OUT OF COURSE)<br><a href="http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/sol.asp" target=_new>http://eq.castersrealm.com/spells/sol.asp</a><br>BST get spells at 9/15/22/30/39/49/50/52/54/55/56/58/59/60 I'M NOT SURE IF THAT'S THE SAME WITH ALL HYBRIDS BUT IT SEEMS LIKELY<br>MOST EVERYTHING ELSE I CAN OFFER IS PURE SPECULATION, BUT I'D THINK IT'S LIKELY THAT THE PET IS SOME KIND OF LARGE CAT LIKE A TIGER, PANTHER, ETC.  THEY WILL ALSO LIKELY HAVE SEVERAL MONK SKILLS. FEIGN DEATH IS UP IN THE AIR.  FOR BALANCING PURPOSES I'D GUESS THAT THEY WON'T GET FEIGN DEATH (BESIDES FD PROBABLY WOULD KILL PET AND THAT WOULD REALLY SUCK IF YOU ACCIDENTALLY HIT HOTKEY AFTER SPENDING LOTS OF MANA SUMMONING/BUFFING PET)  I'D GUESS VAH SHIR GET SAFE FALL, BUT IF NOT IT'S LIKELY THAT BEASTMASTER WILL ANYWAY.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
